  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You quickly replace yourself with an object, allowing you a swifter escape with smaller margins for error. When you would take damage you may increase your AC by +3 until the beginning of your next turn. If this bonus would cause the triggering attack to miss, you may move up to half of your movement away. If you activate this jutsu as a result of making a saving throw, you must still make the saving throw even if your movement would move you to the outside of its range.</p>",
